...ladies and gentlemen,
here we are...

01:03:47.083 --> 01:03:49.875
...in the tomb of Pakal.

01:03:52.583 --> 01:03:56.916
Pakal's body was
with different kind of jewels...

01:03:57.500 --> 01:04:01.250
